spells.description:
Equip: Your attacks have a chance to call to the pact, exploding for 128,163 Shadow damage split between nearby enemies and increasing your Haste by 861 for 10 sec.

Your death breaks the pact, causing a violent explosion.

Equip: The gland releases pheromones that attract a Ceaseless Swarm of insects to surround you. Taking damage has a high chance to retaliate against attackers, inflicting 96,750 Nature damage over 6 sec and reducing damage dealt to you by 29,279.
Equip: Your gear cools with Woven Duskthread and gains 756 Versatility when over 80% health.
